			<h1>Web Footprint (Sites)</h1>
      <p>The Web Footprint determines country and regional sites important to the experience, taking into consideration implications to SEO and domain strategy.</p>
      <h2>Recommendations</h2>
      <p class="lead">JohnsonControls.com should absorb Tyco ‘country’ sites.</p>
      <p>Existing brand and domain authority will sustain findability and organic traffic through transition. Robust redirect strategy maps legacy SEO value to JohnsonControls.com destinations.</p>
      <p class="lead">Maintain JohnsonControls.com subfolder URL structure for international language and country.</p>
      <p>Example: <samp>johnsoncontrols.com/<mark>es_mx</mark></samp></p>
      <p>New Country Code Top Level Domains (ccTLDs) for Johnson Controls start from zero in search.</p>
      <p class="lead">Phase out Tyco sites with no matching JohnsonControls.com language/country subfolders, with these exceptions:</p>
      <p>Spain (<samp><mark>es_es</mark></samp>)<br>Belgium (<samp><mark>be_nl</mark></samp>)</p>
